---
title: How to customize the PersonalBlog starter's appearance
subTitle: GatsbyJS starter instruction
cover: photo-1463852247062-1bbca38f7805-cover.jpg
---

The [starter](/gatsby-starter-personal-blog/) uses a theme object so base customization is really easy.

Find the `theme.js` file.

```text
root
  ├── src
  │   ├── styles
  │   │   ├── colors.js
  │   │   ├── globals.js
  │   │   └── theme.js
```

...

#### Front-end web development

...

title: About
---


I am a graduate from BK Birla Institute of Engineering & Technology Pilani, India, with a B.Tech in Information Technology. I am active in the filed of Web Technology, Renewable Energy(Solar), Electronics, Robotics, and Running.

## My Interests:
* Web Development
* Renewable Energy
* Robotics 
* Running

## My Projects:
  * MPPT Controller
  * [Energy monitoring System](https://data.okosengineering.com/)
  * [Open Robotics Board](https://github.com/vkylamba/Open-Robotics-Board)
  * [Open IoT Development Board](https://github.com/vkylamba/openiotboard)
